CodeGraph (@colbymchenry/codegraph)
    https://github.com/colbymchenry/codegraph
    Licensed under the MIT License.

    The `semgraph` crate's native indexer (src/semgraph, issue #78 Phase 2) is
    interoperable with the schema-v4 `codegraph.db` SQLite format produced by
    CodeGraph, and its per-language tree-sitter definition-extraction queries
    (src/semgraph/src/queries/*.scm) are adapted from CodeGraph's MIT-licensed
    tree-sitter tag queries. The node/edge kind vocabulary, `"<kind>:<hash>"`
    node-id convention, and `::`-joined qualified-name convention follow
    CodeGraph's observed output so that sempkg-built graphs and CodeGraph-built
    graphs are read by the same reader.

